      • getBase64DeserializedObject

        public static <T> T getBase64DeserializedObject​(Cursor cursor,
                                                int columnIndex)
        Deserializes a base64 string contined in the cursor to the templated Object.

        The object must have previously been serialized using the Base64Serialization utility class.

        Type Parameters:
        T - The Type of Object to be Deserialized.
        Parameters:
        columnIndex - index of the column containing the base64 string to be deserialized
        cursor - the cursor containing the column
        Returns:
        An Object of type T or null
